Who else can I be?

16
00:01:56,310 --> 00:01:58,040
 How much did Lin Jing pay you for this job? 

17
00:01:58,040 --> 00:02:00,610
 After tax, several millions. 

18
00:02:00,610 --> 00:02:02,850
 Your project is big, time-consuming, 

19
00:02:02,850 --> 00:02:04,640
 and I heard you have very high standards. 

20
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:06,280
 Most people can't meet them. 

21
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:08,470
 But don't worry, if you choose me, 

22
00:02:08,470 --> 00:02:11,520
 my services will exceed your expectations. 

23
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:13,630
 Tell me what style you like. 

24
00:02:13,630 --> 00:02:16,660
 I always adapt to my client's preferences. 

25
00:02:17,310 --> 00:02:19,520
 I can also show you some of my past work. 

26
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:21,280
 How could that be my first time? 

27
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:23,500
 I've been working in this industry for three years. 

28
00:02:26,730 --> 00:02:30,730
So, everything you said before was about interior design?

29
00:02:35,060 --> 00:02:38,670
I just want to take on your project.

30
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:44,480
Fu Yancheng.

31
