I admit...

32
00:02:49,050 --> 00:02:53,560
I was quite lowly in front of you.

33
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:55,680
That's because I really wanted to get your project,

34
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:59,660
I... I still have my dignity.

35
