 - Goodbye. 

50
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:24,940
I'm sorry, President Fu. I didn't know you were in a meeting.

51
00:04:24,940 --> 00:04:26,430
How are you feeling?

52
00:04:26,430 --> 00:04:28,620
Does your head still hurt?

53
00:04:28,620 --> 00:04:32,430
 What happened? He seems like a totally different person. 

54
00:04:32,430 --> 00:04:33,870
I'm sorry, President Fu.

55
00:04:33,870 --> 00:04:36,800
Even though I don't remember what happened last night,

56
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:39,510
I'm sure I caused you quite a lot of trouble.

57
00:04:39,510 --> 00:04:41,360
I didn't mean to do that.

58
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:43,600
- You... 
 - I'll leave you to your work. I'll leave now.

59
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:45,460
Wait.

60
00:04:46,880 --> 00:04:48,350
Didn't you want to find a working partner?

61
00:04:48,350 --> 00:04:50,800
I can give you a chance to enter a bid.

62
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:53,160
Really?

63
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:56,340
The bidding conference for Royal View Gardens is in three days.

64
00:04:57,510 --> 00:05:00,220
I can give you a chance to prove yourself.

65
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:03,600
You read my design proposal?

66
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:05,920
Your concept is excellent.

67
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:07,530
Thank you.

68
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:15,760
Thank you, President Fu.

69
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:38,080
How is it? Does this breakfast suit your taste?

70
00:05:38,080 --> 00:05:39,880
It's good.

71
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:48,000
- Grandfather. 
  - You brat, you took over Fu Group, 

72
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:50,280
and now you show me no respect.

73
00:05:50,280 --> 00:05:51,830
That's not true, Grandfather

74
00:05:51,830 --> 00:05:54,900
 No? Then why are you trying to divorce Sheng Mian? 

75
00:05:54,900 --> 00:05:58,310
 I may be meditating in the mountains, but I know everything. 

76
00:05:58,310 --> 00:05:59,700
I'll be back tomorrow,

77
00:05:59,700 --> 00:06:03,000
and then we're going to have a good talk.

78
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,630
 Come with me to pick up Grandfather tomorrow. 

79
00:06:10,630 --> 00:06:15,270
 If you don't want a fight, you'd better not mention that we're getting a divorce. 

80
00:06:24,830 --> 00:06:26,210
 Okay, no problem. 

81
00:06:26,210 --> 00:06:28,510
 I'll be there on time. 

82
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:37,050
President Fu, what's the matter?

83
00:06:37,050 --> 00:06:39,070
You don't feel well?

84
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:47,490
It's nothing, just some troublesome issues and troublesome people.

85
00:06:55,970 --> 00:06:58,120
 Fu Yancheng hates his wife so much, 

86
00:06:58,120 --> 00:07:00,920
 I can't let him recognize that I am Penny, 

87
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:03,680
 or it will definitely ruin our cooperation. 

88
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:06,760
 I'll just show up today, and put on a show with him. 

89
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:34,560
Hello?

90
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,160
Dad.

91
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:56,950
 Your sister is in the hospital again. Come quickly. 

92
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:58,900
I'll be there right away.

93
00:08:03,070 --> 00:08:06,600
 Sorry, the number you have dialed cannot be connected at the moment. 

94
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:08,270
 Please... 

95
00:08:11,750 --> 00:08:16,630
Grandfather, you look better after your retreat in the mountains.

96
00:08:16,630 --> 00:08:21,730
Brat, you sure know how to make people happy.

97
00:08:22,750 --> 00:08:25,000
Where's Sheng Mian?

98
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:27,000
Is she busy?

99
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:30,030
Who knows? Maybe she came down with acute appendicitis,

100
00:08:30,030 --> 00:08:32,000
or met with an accident on her way.

101
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:35,870
You brat! What are you saying? Hey!

102
00:08:35,870 --> 00:08:37,790
Seriously.

103
00:08:37,790 --> 00:08:41,290
What kind of nonsense are you spewing?

104
00:08:41,290 --> 00:08:42,960
You just came back in such good condition from your recuperation.

105
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:45,720
Let's not mention her, it's bad luck.

106
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:55,030
Mian Mian, I'm so happy you came today.

107
00:08:55,030 --> 00:08:57,480
And you've even brought me a gift.

108
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:59,910
That's so nice of you, I like it very much.

109
00:08:59,910 --> 00:09:01,670
I'm so happy you like it.

110
00:09:01,670 --> 00:09:05,200
I was planning to pick you up with Yancheng that day,

111
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:06,910
but there was an urgent family matter that came up.

112
00:09:06,910 --> 00:09:08,790
I'm so sorry.

113
00:09:08,790 --> 00:09:13,000
Silly girl, you don't have to treat me as an outsider.

114
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:15,200
I'm not a temperamental person.

115
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:18,830
It's such a pity Yancheng isn't home today.

116
00:09:19,790 --> 00:09:23,060
Why do you always come when he isn't around?

117
00:09:23,750 --> 00:09:25,960
Have you two been fighting?

118
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:28,390
No, Grandfather.

119
