doesn't really smile much?

122
00:09:36,670 --> 00:09:39,480
Yancheng has actually been through a lot.

123
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:43,000
As a child, his parents were always busy.

124
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:45,080
So, he has always been alone.

125
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:48,000
He can be prideful and aloof,

126
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:50,910
but that's all the surface.

127
00:09:50,910 --> 00:09:53,480
He doesn't know how to express his feelings.

128
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:55,110
But, actually, he's a warm person.

129
00:09:55,110 --> 00:09:57,720
He values feelings very much!

130
00:09:57,720 --> 00:10:02,790
So, I want you to give him a little time and get to know him.

131
00:10:02,790 --> 00:10:04,790
I will do that, Grandfather.

132
00:10:04,790 --> 00:10:09,200
