134
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:15,440
Grandfather, you're strong and healthy.

135
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:17,750
You'll definitely meet your grandchildren.

136
00:10:17,750 --> 00:10:19,250
Good!

137
00:10:19,870 --> 00:10:23,270
I'm so happy to hear that.

138
00:10:23,270 --> 00:10:27,280
Yancheng has always caused me to worry.

139
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:30,380
