144
00:10:38,730 --> 00:10:41,010
You have to be good to her.

145
00:10:41,630 --> 00:10:43,480
 Oh, no. 

146
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:46,640
 Fu Yancheng is going to be angry again. 

147
00:10:49,630 --> 00:10:51,390
Qi Chen, take me to Grandfather's house.

148
00:10:51,390 --> 00:10:53,120
But, President Fu, we have an appointment with President Zhang.

149
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,370
I'll see him later.

150
00:10:54,370 --> 00:10:55,770
Okay.

151
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:05,550
Yancheng heard that you're here, so he's on his way over.

152
